@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.15 * v2 + 0.23)) / v2)
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = 0.44
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.94 * v2 + 0.60) - (v2 + 0.35 / v1 + 0.01)))
    v2 = 0.88
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
